Ouliners

  • Don't follow the general trend

  • Badly Impact the following algorithms because we calculate weight here

    • Linear Regression
    • Logistic Regression
    • AdaBoost
    • Deep Learning

  • How to detect outliners


  • Normal Distribution


  • Skewed Distribution

  • Other Distributioon

Techniques to detect and remove Outliners


  1. Z-Score-

    • Apply where the data is Normally Distributed or close to Normally Distributed

    • Now we can do two things
      • Trim the ouliners
      • Set a capping limit to our data

  1. IQR-

    • Apply only when data distribution is skewed


  1. Based on Percentile
    • Consider all the data above 99 percentile and below 1 percentile to be considered as outliners
    • We can again trim those outliners or set a capping limit to them
    • In case of Percentile when we do capping then this process is called Winsorization
